218
00:14:18,566 --> 00:14:20,359
Você realmente ficou louca?

219
00:14:20,442 --> 00:14:21,944
Talvez.

220
00:14:23,070 --> 00:14:24,572
Eu sempre quis

221
00:14:25,531 --> 00:14:26,740
